    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏最初发售版将仅支持英文，敬请谅解。</strong><br><br>一支小队，一项任务，一个计划。将这些元素拼凑在一起，一场经典的劫案便已成型——只是得有“惊喜”才足够精彩。你的小队成员来自非洲不同国家，都是干着普普通通工作的平凡市民。任务则是盗回西方博物馆中的非洲文物。至于计划？那就要看你发挥了。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/221b337e541e15ad0ff57ee14e317230.poster.avif?t=1771833572\" width=1170 height=474 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/221b337e541e15ad0ff57ee14e317230.webm?t=1771833572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/221b337e541e15ad0ff57ee14e317230.mp4?t=1771833572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">非洲未来主义盗窃</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >21世纪末期，各大政治势力斡旋促成了《跨大西洋回归条约》，承诺将各博物馆收藏的非洲文物归还本国。传统的外交手段一度看似进展顺利，但形势急转直下。一项修正案突然更改了文物归还的具体条款，各大博物馆在得知只需归还公开展出的文物后，开始慢慢地将这些珍宝从展览中撤下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >既然生活总给你出难题，博物馆又暗地里耍花招，那就干脆以牙还牙，尝试更加隐秘的全新“外交”手段。你需要夺回70件文物，每一件都存在于现实世界，对其原属族群承载着无可估量的文化、历史与精神价值。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/f2a5fdb6600843e832e7e7d2d4d55765.poster.avif?t=1771833572\" width=1170 height=474 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/f2a5fdb6600843e832e7e7d2d4d55765.webm?t=1771833572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/f2a5fdb6600843e832e7e7d2d4d55765.mp4?t=1771833572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">团队协作决定成败</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切开始于某个爱惹麻烦的小兄弟，没错，他老是把你拖进各种烂摊子。还好，你——诺马利——将会遇到来自非洲各国的靠谱队友。你招募的人员既有经典黑客，也有……古板正经的老奶奶？别担心，老奶奶也能独当一面。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/92f53814d115b9a14697e1c990d89f3b.poster.avif?t=1771833572\" width=1170 height=474 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/92f53814d115b9a14697e1c990d89f3b.webm?t=1771833572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/92f53814d115b9a14697e1c990d89f3b.mp4?t=1771833572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">提前踩点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提前为顺利脱身做好规划。检查撤离路线，设法破解谜题和障碍，找出关键位置，招募合适的队友助你一臂之力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/db8ff3c8aea764913edcf1db223d2f5a.poster.avif?t=1771833572\" width=1170 height=474 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/db8ff3c8aea764913edcf1db223d2f5a.webm?t=1771833572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/db8ff3c8aea764913edcf1db223d2f5a.mp4?t=1771833572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">有进有出</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你做好了精心布置，而文物就美美地等着——摆出一副让人无从下手的样子，但别担心，很快就能搞定——行动的时候到了。将文物从放置点拿走的瞬间，倒计时便会开启。而凭借诺马利行云流水般的的跑酷能力，逃脱过程将如同身处劫盗大片中最过瘾的蒙太奇片段。但如果你在规划阶段有所懈怠，那可要付出代价了！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/d324b64ce6c871be874361178332a27c.poster.avif?t=1771833572\" width=1170 height=474 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/d324b64ce6c871be874361178332a27c.webm?t=1771833572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255890/extras/d324b64ce6c871be874361178332a27c.mp4?t=1771833572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>上演惊天劫案：</strong>通过破解谜题、巧妙部署队友，精心规划你的逃离路线。做好准备后，再凭借诺马利行云流水般的跑酷能力带着文物溜之大吉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>招募队员：</strong>结识身怀绝技的各路人马，逐步招揽他们加入你的小队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>探索非洲未来主义世界：</strong>据点设于南非，你将在此一睹未来约翰内斯堡的奇幻景象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>夺回真实文物：</strong>寻回70件现实中存在的珍贵文物，每一件都对其原属族群承载着无可估量的文化、历史与精神价值。</p>",
